Notes taking application

Home page (/ route)
    Jitne bhi notes wo show honge => description
    New note (button) => new page ( /new )

/ new
    form
        title
        description
        Submit (button) => server pr ek request jaegi note create krne ki => user ko wapis home page redirect (/ route)

/edit/:title
    form
     title (data already fill hoga)
     description (data already fill hoga)
     update => server => update => redirect (/)

/delete/:title
    server => delete => redirect (/)